  "detailed_description": "In this wholesome community-focused adventure, Cloudi is tasked with restoring nature to its original pristine state. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381040/extras/a448a1d3986c30b8a99395cd1390d814.poster.avif?t=1742422779\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381040/extras/a448a1d3986c30b8a99395cd1390d814.webm?t=1742422779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381040/extras/a448a1d3986c30b8a99395cd1390d814.mp4?t=1742422779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This is accomplished by cultivating and upgrading an assortment of magical crops.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381040/extras/e9b076285e2a133a8de934858aa64f16.poster.avif?t=1742422779\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381040/extras/e9b076285e2a133a8de934858aa64f16.webm?t=1742422779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381040/extras/e9b076285e2a133a8de934858aa64f16.mp4?t=1742422779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>However, watch out for the slobsters - they don’t take kindly to a clean environment!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381040/extras/fa4ae82b8d7c649e564d7de3392a79c6.poster.avif?t=1742422779\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381040/extras/fa4ae82b8d7c649e564d7de3392a79c6.webm?t=1742422779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381040/extras/fa4ae82b8d7c649e564d7de3392a79c6.mp4?t=1742422779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Luckily, Cloudi has a squad of loyal friends to help out.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381040/extras/7deb1714510a681f566c87055c303d0d.poster.avif?t=1742422779\" width=620 height=325 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381040/extras/7deb1714510a681f566c87055c303d0d.webm?t=1742422779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Features of Cirrus Business</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Story-Driven Farming:</strong> Experience a unique farming simulator that weaves an engaging narrative with several possible endings.<br></li><li><strong>Dynamic Farming System:</strong> Manage upgradeable crops in a highly dynamic system, requiring players to balance enemy generation and resource production for a challenging yet rewarding experience.<br></li><li><strong>Character Abilities:</strong> Each character comes with unique abilities intricately interwoven into the farming system, adding layers of strategy to the gameplay.<br></li><li><strong>Community Focus:</strong> Immerse yourself in a heartwarming sense of neighborly community, enhanced by cutscenes that bring characters together and unfold a coherent story.<br></li><li><strong>Handcrafted Aesthetics:</strong> Enjoy a cozy aesthetic as all assets and music are created from scratch, contributing to a heartfelt gaming experience. :)</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "In this wholesome community-focused adventure, Cloudi is tasked with restoring nature to its original pristine state. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381040/extras/a448a1d3986c30b8a99395cd1390d814.poster.avif?t=1742422779\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381040/extras/a448a1d3986c30b8a99395cd1390d814.webm?t=1742422779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381040/extras/a448a1d3986c30b8a99395cd1390d814.mp4?t=1742422779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This is accomplished by cultivating and upgrading an assortment of magical crops.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381040/extras/e9b076285e2a133a8de934858aa64f16.poster.avif?t=1742422779\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381040/extras/e9b076285e2a133a8de934858aa64f16.webm?t=1742422779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381040/extras/e9b076285e2a133a8de934858aa64f16.mp4?t=1742422779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>However, watch out for the slobsters - they don’t take kindly to a clean environment!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381040/extras/fa4ae82b8d7c649e564d7de3392a79c6.poster.avif?t=1742422779\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381040/extras/fa4ae82b8d7c649e564d7de3392a79c6.webm?t=1742422779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381040/extras/fa4ae82b8d7c649e564d7de3392a79c6.mp4?t=1742422779\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Luckily, Cloudi has a squad of loyal friends to help out.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381040/extras/7deb1714510a681f566c87055c303d0d.poster.avif?t=1742422779\" width=620 height=325 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2381040/extras/7deb1714510a681f566c87055c303d0d.webm?t=1742422779\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Features of Cirrus Business</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Story-Driven Farming:</strong> Experience a unique farming simulator that weaves an engaging narrative with several possible endings.<br></li><li><strong>Dynamic Farming System:</strong> Manage upgradeable crops in a highly dynamic system, requiring players to balance enemy generation and resource production for a challenging yet rewarding experience.<br></li><li><strong>Character Abilities:</strong> Each character comes with unique abilities intricately interwoven into the farming system, adding layers of strategy to the gameplay.<br></li><li><strong>Community Focus:</strong> Immerse yourself in a heartwarming sense of neighborly community, enhanced by cutscenes that bring characters together and unfold a coherent story.<br></li><li><strong>Handcrafted Aesthetics:</strong> Enjoy a cozy aesthetic as all assets and music are created from scratch, contributing to a heartfelt gaming experience. :)</li></ul>",
